OL,3,CMoment vehicle stop leads to discovery
OL,4,Cof drugs and weapons
OL,6,FA vehicle stop in Bristol resulted in
OL,7,Fpolice finding bags of drugs and
OL,8,Floaded weapons.
OL,10,FAround 4.30pm on Wednesday 2 October
OL,11,Flast year, officers stopped a black
OL,12,FBMW on Bond Street as it was suspected
OL,13,Fof driving using a cloned number plate.
OL,15,FThe front seat passenger, Sepehr
OL,16,FYousefali, informed officers he had a
OL,17,Floaded firearm in the waistband of his
OL,18,Ftrousers. Officers located the firearm
OL,19,Fon Yousefali.
