OL,3,CMoment vehicle stop leads to discovery
OL,4,Cof drugs and weapons
OL,6,FDavid Meti was driving and police
OL,7,Ffound a machete between his seat and
OL,8,Fthe door.
OL,10,FA further search led officers to
OL,11,Fdiscover two carrier bags of drugs,
OL,12,Fincluding cocaine, cannabis, MDMA and
OL,13,Fketamine.
OL,15,FBoth offenders were arrested and taken
OL,16,Finto police custody. The drugs were
OL,17,Ftested and officers established the
OL,18,Fdrugs held an estimated street value
OL,19,Fof almost #6,000.
