OL,3,CMoment vehicle stop leads to discovery
OL,4,Cof drugs and weapons
OL,6,FYousefali, aged 22 of no fixed
OL,7,Faddress, and Meti, aged 22 and from
OL,8,FLondon, both pleaded guilty to all
OL,9,Fcharges put to them. This included
OL,10,Fthree counts of possession with intent
OL,11,Fto supply class A drugs and two counts
OL,12,Fof possession with intent to supply
OL,13,Fclass B drugs.
OL,15,FYousefali was additionally charged
OL,16,Fwith and pleaded guilty to three
OL,17,Ffirearms offences.
