OL,6,FAt the sentencing, Yousefali was
OL,7,Fjailed for eight years and nine months
OL,8,Fand Meti was handed a four-year prison
OL,9,Fsentence.
OL,11,FSenior Investigating Officer DI
OL,12,FNicholas Lawson said: "It is clear
OL,13,Ffrom the weapons Yousefali and Meti
OL,14,Fhad in their possession that they had
OL,15,Fthe potential to cause serious harm.
