OL,6,F"The pair were transporting a
OL,7,Fsignificant amount of illegal drugs,
OL,8,Fthat no doubt would have ended up on
OL,9,Fthe streets of Bristol had officers
OL,10,Fnot wisely taken the proactive action
OL,11,Fto stop the vehicle.
OL,13,F"Our enquiries found they were
OL,14,Fdeliberately targeting people who
OL,15,Fenjoy Bristol's night-time economy and
OL,16,Fseeking to profit from the misery that
OL,17,Fsuch substances cause.
